Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:09.24,White-双语,,0,0,0,,{\fs120}阿杰！暮暮！救命！\N{\fs60}APPLEJACK! TWILIGHT! HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:12.04,White-双语,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你们了，我什么坏事都没做！\N{\fs60}I'm telling you, I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:16.51,White-双语,,0,0,0,,请问能不能…让我来为她辩护？\N{\fs60}What if be alright if I led this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:21.04,White-双语,,0,0,0,,我叫隐秘眼眸，是本案的首席调查员。\N{\fs60}My name is Private Eye. I'm the lead investigator for this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:25.77,White-双语,,0,0,0,,受害者名叫皇家秩序，是塞拉斯蒂娅公主的皇家卫队中的一员。\N{\fs60}The victim's name is Royal Order, a member of Princess Celestia's royal guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.66,White-双语,,0,0,0,,那个飞板…！还有那个货斗…！都是飞板璐的东西！\N{\fs60}That scooter…! And that wagon…! Those are Scootaloo's!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.86,White-双语,,0,0,0,,那么，这就是梦魇之月雕像了吧？\N{\fs60}So, this is the Nightmare Night statue, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.64,White-双语,,0,0,0,,真的{\fs120}曾{\fs}有更多血迹！\N{\fs60}There really WAS more blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:35.64,White-双语,,0,0,0,,这并{\fs100}不是{\fs}皇家秩序的血。\N{\fs60}This ISN'T Royal Order's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.68,White-双语,,0,0,0,,你是说这案子…可能有{\fs100}第二个{\fs}受害者？\N{\fs60} You mean this case… might have a SECOND victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:41.37,White-双语,,0,0,0,,我们会想办法证明飞板璐的清白。\N{\fs60}We'll find a way to prove Scootaloo's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.82,White-双语,,0,0,0,,好吧，你最好说到做到。因为…\N{\fs60}Okay. You better. Because…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:48.24,White-双语,,0,0,0,,如果你们做不到，我会自己想办法，无论何种方式…\N{\fs60}If you don't, I'll find a way to do it myself. No matter what…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:49.14,White-双语,,0,0,0,,一言为定。\N{\fs60}It's a deal.
