Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.17,1:21:40.06,White-双语,,0,0,0,,所以，她拒绝了你的辩护提议？\N{\fs60}So, she turned down your request to defend her?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.06,1:21:44.68,White-双语,,0,0,0,,是的。如今，她，以及新的嫌疑犯\N{\fs60}Yes. Instead, she, and the new suspect
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.68,1:21:47.57,White-双语,,0,0,0,,选择了那些人类律师中的一员。\N{\fs60}have opted for one of those human attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.57,1:21:49.57,White-双语,,0,0,0,,…那公主呢？\N{\fs60}…And what of the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.57,1:21:53.10,White-双语,,0,0,0,,目前来看她会再一次帮助辩护方。\N{\fs60}It seems as if she will be aiding the defense once more.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.81,1:21:57.71,White-双语,,0,0,0,,那，你现在要我做什么？\N{\fs60}So, what will you have me do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.71,1:22:03.86,White-双语,,0,0,0,,我不想多嘴，但看上去我们要盖不住这些秘密了。\N{\fs50}I hate to say it, but it’s starting to look like we won’t be able to keep these secrets much longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.86,1:22:09.80,White-双语,,0,0,0,,确实。现在，回小马镇，继续你的调查吧。\N{\fs60}Indeed. For now, return to Ponyville, and continue the investigation on your end.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.80,1:22:14.13,White-双语,,0,0,0,,有我的许可，卫兵不会阻拦你进入案发现场。\N{\fs60}The guards will not bar you from the scene, so long as you have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.13,1:22:15.24,White-双语,,0,0,0,,是，大人。\N{\fs60}Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.86,1:22:24.84,White-双语,,0,0,0,,哼。\N{\fs60}Hmph.
